{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, nobody said what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But most of the time they loved-- they enjoyed made us count the lashes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, in the middle of the count, you also had the yelling, oh, it hurts, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So bestial, as they were, they enjoyed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recall in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the times when two particular guys ran away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot their names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wrote a book about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the only, I think-- at least what I think-- the only two guys who ran off and made it, and really notified the world on what's going on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, of course, that was for them, devastating to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were staying in appell-- which is the line-up-- for the whole afternoon, the whole evening through the middle of the next day, while they were going around with the dogs to try to find them, until they called it off.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because to us, it meant extreme punishments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they can't find them, you know, they gave us the portion, to teach us a lesson what happens to you the next time if somebody runs away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "During the time when you were in Kanada, did you ever-- as far as the transports that would come in and stuff, do you ever remember seeing or hearing of a transport from your hometown?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no such a thing anymore, because my-- my hometown was emptied out in 1942 and in 1943.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all the transports that came in right now, they came in from-- from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, in Kanada, itself, had no contact whatsoever with people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every once in a while, maybe, somebody came up with a suitcase, with a name that somebody may-- might have known, but it was very rare.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
